50|$|In 2009, E {{gathered}} {{an ensemble}} cast of six of Korea's top female thespians (Youn Yuh-jung, Lee Mi-sook, Go Hyun-jung, Choi Ji-woo, Kim Min-hee, Kim Ok-bin) for his low-budget, semi-improvisational mockumentary Actresses. Set during a fashion magazine shoot on Christmas Eve, the film depicted the celebrity and humanity of actresses, {{with the cast}} all using their real-life names and telling candid stories. It became the third of E's creations {{to be invited to}} the <b>Berlin</b> <b>International</b> <b>Film</b> <b>Festival's</b> Panorama section.|$|R
